title: Windows 10 Pro VL X86 MULTi-17 March 2016 {Generation2}
description:
* Windows 10 Pro VL X86 MULTi-17 March 2016 {Generation2}


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* This release contains one ISO [SOURCE ISO] and sixteen executable svf-files.

* All exe-files are created from 
* 10586.0.151029-1700.TH2_RELEASE_CLIENTPROFESSIONALVL_VOL_X86FRE

* This is done with SmartVersion, a program that calculates the
* difference between two files (one of which is used as the source)
* and then creates an svf-file based on that difference.

* Screenshots:
[url]http://server.myspace-shack.com/d21/11136624.png[/url]

* Hashes & sources attached in a separate .txt

[ DOWNLOAD INFO ]

* Download the Source ISO and preferred language.exe

* If you want en-US then just download the SOURCE ISO

* Run the exe-file in the same folder as the SOURCE ISO.
* This will extract the ORIGINAL ISO in the selected language.

[ CONTENTS ]

[ SOURCE ISO ]

* Win10.X86.en-US.iso - 3.23GB

* Integrated / Pre-installed:

* KB3135782
* KB3139907
* KB3140743

* Setupcomplete / Post-install:

* .NET Framework 3.5
* KB890830
* Defender Updates

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ]

* Windows 10 Pro
* Windows 10 Pro - - - - - Pre-Activated

* Screenshots:
[url]http://server.myspace-shack.com/d21/20160306.png[/url]
